---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Products"
  description="Selected digital health and AI products across endoscopy and radiology."
>
  <Section title="Products">
    <div class="list">
      <article class="item">
        <h3>Endoscopy Workflow Management</h3>
        <p>
          At Olympus, I work on endoscopy workflow management, including reporting, documentation,
          workflow automation, voice reporting, structured data capture, and interoperability with
          hospital systems.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <h3>OLYSENSE / Intelligent Endoscopy</h3>
        <p>
          I have worked on AI-enabled gastrointestinal endoscopy topics, including detection,
          diagnosis, and quality-related applications. The emphasis is moving from standalone
          algorithms toward connected workflow systems.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <h3>AI Endoscopy Products</h3>
        <p>
          My work includes product management for AI functionality in endoscopy use cases, aligned
          with medical software requirements and clinical workflow needs.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <h3>AI-Rad Companion</h3>
        <p>
          At Siemens Healthineers, I worked on AI products for radiology image analysis, including
          regulated clinical applications.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <h3>AI-Rad Companion Chest X-ray</h3>
        <p>
          I worked on AI-Rad Companion Chest X-ray as part of product management for chest X-ray
          diagnosis workflows. The scope included clinical evaluation, regulatory evidence, and
          product development.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
